{"tid":816462,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得per se好高汁","createTime":"2018-09-12T18:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T07:07:01.000Z","uid":29021,"like":38,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"21a486a9b5f6be342c19ac89ab6ada7b264cff88","tid":816462,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:29:19.000Z","msg":"首先要介紹嘅一定係呢首，聽完真係返唔到轉頭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jUvDfKjI_TY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjUvDfKjI_TY&d=Q%2FdHQiWXcl66RpyTsZ%2FmRDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=2f523f21\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jUvDfKjI_TY</a><br />\n《家變》 - per se<br />\n<br />\n先嚟一節鋼琴前奏，立即將你嘅注意力放入首歌嘅意境入面，尤其最尾嗰句，真係不得不佩服佢個編曲，已經正到喊出嚟。之後 Stephen 嘅聲真係非常有吸引力，馬上有種上癮嘅感覺，副歌個假音更加係神來之筆，聽完我都唔記得自己loop咗幾多次<br />\n<br />\nper se都係近期先至有廣東歌，所以喺聽佢另一首《親愛的幽靈》之前，聽吓其他早期多少少嘅歌先：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bSL_McTQvbA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbSL_McTQvbA&d=Q%2FdHQiWXcl66RpyTsZ%2FmRDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=80e4cdcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bSL_McTQvbA</a><br />\nMonocircus - per se<br />\n<br />\n呢首歌幾乎可以話係per se嘅出道作，佢地就係憑呢首歌拎到2014年通利琴行原音樂隊比賽金獎。呢首歌最特別嘅地方就係佢嘅英式搖滾曲風，清新得嚟富有層次感，雖然係早期作品但係一啲都唔失色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cqKhYh0mAsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcqKhYh0mAsc&d=Q%2FdHQiWXcl66RpyTsZ%2FmRDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=88cf270b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cqKhYh0mAsc</a><br />\nthe mist - per se<br />\n<br />\n呢首係收錄咗喺佢地第二隻專輯Conundrum入面，最搶嘅唔係Stephen把聲，而係極之靚嘅歌詞。話晒係「詩式音樂」，點少得有詩意嘅歌詞同曲譜呢？呢首歌簡直係完美示範咗per se嘅獨特風格，絕對係我嘅favorite之一。<br />\n<br />\n講真，佢地好多歌都極之高質，唔聽真係唔覺得香港竟然會有啲咁嘅清泉。就好似毒品一樣會上癮嘅，除咗辦教育（羅范椒芬，2004）同埋港獨（陳勇，2018）之外，仲有per se。"},{"pid":"01b076c38154382483174d36bc1760df8a2cfdbf","tid":816462,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:31:29.000Z","msg":"以為iPhone 出返se<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b7f9eb10d97895989f93080c92526042e14332","tid":816462,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b076c38154382483174d36bc1760df8a2cfdbf","tid":816462,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:31:29.000Z","msg":"以為iPhone 出返se<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:35:30.000Z","msg":"音樂台嚟㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee823dbaa3770d28a085463426de796ac5362fb","tid":816462,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T21:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa70bf06fe30c94c7fea415df2f14d173990d47e","tid":816462,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84898f18c5ae34ffaad05e811fd03ea6e47e1046","tid":816462,"uid":65859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:35:25.000Z","msg":"中意perse既話，可以聽下凜冽時雨，個風格都似"},{"pid":"46e50cfdd8a80a056b910c5e2cd8fb2768d3783f","tid":816462,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84898f18c5ae34ffaad05e811fd03ea6e47e1046","tid":816462,"uid":65859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:35:25.000Z","msg":"中意perse既話，可以聽下凜冽時雨，個風格都似"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"per se啲編曲太POP,可能係要就香港聽眾(?<br />\n都係凜冽時雨正啲rock啲"},{"pid":"7b22aab94a3814030a310f276851cdf863b82ed